OL,3,C'Heartless' thief jailed after
OL,4,Ctargeting couple with newborn baby
OL,6,FA career criminal stole a purse from a
OL,7,Fcar belonging to a couple with a
OL,8,Fnewborn baby.
OL,10,FMichael Wilson snuck into the Ford S-
OL,11,FMax in the middle on the night after
OL,12,Ffinding it unlocked on a private
OL,13,Fdriveway in Mapperley, in Nottingham.
OL,15,FThe 49-year-old then stole a purse
OL,16,Ffrom inside a large bag containing
OL,17,Fitems for the baby, such as wipes and
OL,18,Fclothes.
