OL,3,C'Heartless' thief jailed after
OL,4,Ctargeting couple with newborn baby
OL,6,FNottingham Crown Court heard he then
OL,7,Ftook a bank card out of the purse and
OL,8,Fused it to buy cigarettes and tobacco
OL,9,Fat several service stations.
OL,11,FPolice recognised him after viewing
OL,12,FCCTV footage and arrested him.
OL,14,FHe initially denied the offences and
OL,15,Fthe matter went to trial, during which
OL,16,Fhe changed his plea and admitted four
OL,17,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,18,Frepresentation and handling stolen
OL,19,Fgoods.
OL,21,FHe has now been jailed for 14 months.
