OL,3,C'Heartless' thief jailed after
OL,4,Ctargeting couple with newborn baby
OL,6,FThe court heard the offences took
OL,7,Fplace in October 2021 and that Wilson,
OL,8,Fof Labray Road, Calverton, was a
OL,9,Fprolific offender.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Julian Eminson-
OL,12,FFerry, of Nottinghamshire Police,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Wilson would have known he was
OL,14,Ftargeting a young family as the bag he
OL,15,Frummaged through had a number of items
OL,16,Ffor the couple's newborn baby.
OL,18,F"Yet he still stole the purse and
OL,19,Fspent the family's hard-earned money
OL,20,Fat a string of locations. I can only
OL,21,Fdescribe him as heartless.
