OL,4,Ctargeting couple with newborn baby
OL,6,F"Such has been the number of times
OL,7,Fwe've had to arrest him, officers
OL,8,Fimmediately recognised him from CCTV
OL,9,Ffootage and put him before the courts.
OL,11,F"Sadly, he continued to show no
OL,12,Fremorse and took the case to trial.
OL,14,F"Owing to the overwhelming evidence
OL,15,Fagainst him, he did finally change his
OL,16,Fpleas to guilty ` and I'm glad he has
OL,17,Fnow been sentenced.
